Package: medRCT
Title: Causal mediation analysis estimating interventional effects mapped to a target trial
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Tong", "Chen", email = "tong.chen@mcri.edu.au", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2751-2412")),
    person("Margarita", "Moreno-Betancur", email = "margarita.moreno@mcri.edu.au", role = "aut"),
    person("S. Ghazaleh", "Dashti", email = "ghazaleh.dashti@mcri.edu.au", role = "aut"))
Description: Package for causal mediation analysis using interventional effects defined by mapping to a target trial assessing hypothetical mediator interventions. The package supports any number of potentially correlated mediators, including mediators that are not of primary interest but that are intermediate (exposure-induced) mediator-outcome confounders.
